 with revenues growing on a comparable basis in both the retail and the wholesale branded sector, and operating margins sustained well despite lower absolute</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742453-caleres-margins-are-returning-to-the-mean-as-warned-still-a-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:35:38"}, {"id": "4742448", "title": "UniCredit: Will It Be The Next Leading EU Bank?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Unicredit Tower skyscraper in Milan\" data-id=\"1014081722\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Cineberg</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Here at the Lab, we have good coverage of EU financial institutions. This year, the sector has already delivered a 31% total return, and the banking industry still trades at a 20% discount to long-run P/E multiple and a 47% discount to the broader market. This</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742448-unicredit-stock-will-it-be-next-leading-eu-bank", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:15:49"}, {"id": "4742445", "title": "Signet: It Has Been Great For Trading, But Not This Time", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stop sign\" data-id=\"157640177\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4368px\" height=\"2912px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 120