ck market and exchange\" data-id=\"2169928982\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2169928982/image_2169928982.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2169928982/image_2169928982.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2169928982/image_2169928982.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2169928982/image_2169928982.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2169928982/image_2169928982.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2169928982/image_2169928982.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2169928982/image_2169928982.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2169928982/image_2169928982.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NVS/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Robinsons Land Corporation (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RBLAF\" title=\"Robinsons Land Corporation\">OTC:RBLAF</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RBLAY\" title=\"Robinsons Land Corporation\">OTCPK:RBLAY</a>) is one of the leading real estate companies in the Philippines. The company's diverse real estate portfolio includes divisions such as Robinsons Residences. Its rental division comprises</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2169928982/image_2169928982.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742441-robinsons-land-undervalued-you-are-just-paying-for-its-land", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 23:44:37"}, {"id": "4742447", "title": "Fed Likely To Cut Rates Again This Month As 2025 View Grows More Cloudy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1938437890/image_1938437890.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Unethical American bank\" data-id=\"1938437890\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1938437890/image_1938437890.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1938437890/image_1938437890.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1938437890/image_1938437890.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1938437890/image_1938437890.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1938437890/image_1938437890.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1938437890/image_1938437890.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1938437890/image_1938437890.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1938437890/image_1938437890.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The US Federal Reserve appears likely to lower benchmark interest rates again later this month, after cutting interest rates at its previous two meetings. The central bank's plans for rates in 2025 are anyone's guess.</p> <p>The Fed</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1938437890/image_1938437890.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742447-fed-likely-to-cut-rates-again-this-month-as-2025-view-grows-more-cloudy", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 23:17:00"}, {"id": "4742430", "title": "Nvidia Q3: Blackwell Ramp Just Started", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838082778/image_838082778.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Blue arrow pointing up from surface\" data-id=\"838082778\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1097px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838082778/image_838082778.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838082778/image_838082778.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838082778/image_838082778.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838082778/image_838082778.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838082778/image_838082778.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838082778/image_838082778.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838082778/image_838082778.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838082778/image_838082778.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Wavebreakmedia/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>NVDA stock: previous thesis and Q3 recap</h2> <p>I last analyzed <strong>Nvidia Corporation </strong>(NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a>) back in October 2024. Under a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4728086-nvidia-latest-blackwell-developments-support-one-stop-ai-shop-scenario\">title</a> of \u201cNvidia: Latest Blackwell Developments Support One-Stop AI Shop Scenario,\u201d I published an article to analyze</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/838082778/image_838082778.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742430-nvidia-q3-blackwell-ramp-just-started", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 23:02:07"}, {"id": "4742428", "title": "MacroGenics: A Productive Biotech With Growing Potential - Still Not A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185328417/image_185328417.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Burst your bubble\" data-id=\"185328417\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1020px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185328417/image_185328417.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185328417/image_185328417.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185328417/image_185328417.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185328417/image_185328417.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185328417/image_185328417.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185328417/image_185328417.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/185328417/image_185328417.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/upload